The '''Egypt Hockey Federation''' ('''EHF''') is the [[sports governing body|governing body]] of [[Field hockey|Field Hockey]] in [[Egypt]]. The Headquarters of EHF are in [[Nasr City]], [[Cairo]]. It is affiliated to IHF [[International Hockey Federation]] and AHF [[African Hockey Federation]].

