'''Honneur Stadium''' ({{Lang-ar|الملعب الشرفي}}) (Stade d'Honneur) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Oujda]], [[Morocco]]. It is used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium has a capacity of 35,000<ref>https://int.soccerway.com/teams/morocco/mouloudia-oujda/3470/venue/</ref> people.
