'''Klaipėdos centrinis stadionas''' is a football stadium in [[Klaipėda]], [[Lithuania]].  It is the home ground of [[FK Atlantas]], and has a capacity of 4,428.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.atlantas.lt/lt/komanda/klaipedos-miesto-centrinis-stadionas|title=FK Atlantas Klaipėda: Klaipėdos M. Centrinis Stadionas|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517130918/http://www.atlantas.lt/lt/komanda/klaipedos-miesto-centrinis-stadionas|archivedate=2016-05-17|df=}}</ref>

