'''Maccabi Ra'anana''' is a professional [[basketball]] club based in [[Ra'anana]], [[Israel]]. Founded in 2011, the club plays in the [[Liga Leumit (basketball)|Liga Leumit]], the second-tier division league of Israel.<ref>[http://basketball.eurobasket.com/team/Israel/Maccabi_Raanana/10044 Maccabi Raanana basketball team – Eurobasket.com]</ref>

